ae2bd80c0695"],

Cell["\<\
When this transformation is applied to the normal distribution, a new \
distribution is obtained characterised by three parameters which control \
mean, variance and skewness.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.777372482547079*^9, 3.7773726227542515`*^9}, {
  3.7833157263867855`*^9, 
